{"tid":160326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"展示缺台灣藏南「中國地圖」捱批 奧迪中國致歉","createTime":"2017-03-17T15:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T00:27:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"435b665c38546f4a2d8666fd9901ee4575502f23","tid":160326,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://china.hket.com/article/1711773/展示缺台灣藏南「中國地圖」捱批%20奧迪中國致歉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1711773%2F%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA%E7%BC%BA%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E8%97%8F%E5%8D%97%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E3%80%8D%E6%8D%B1%E6%89%B9%2520%E5%A5%A7%E8%BF%AA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=c04b14ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://china.hket.com/article/1711773/展示缺台灣藏南「中國地圖」捱批%20奧迪中國致歉</a><br />\n德國汽車品牌奧迪（Audi），被揭日前在總部介紹中國大陸及港澳地區業務時，使用一幅未包含台灣、藏南及及南海諸島等地區的「中國地圖」，引來大批大陸網民抗議。奧迪中國事後發聲明致歉，指「錯誤的地圖傷害了中國人民的感情」，並回應網民稱「我們也有一顆同樣的中國心」。<br />\n<br />\n奧迪前日（15日）在其德國禾夫斯堡總部舉行年度全球記者會，在介紹中國大陸及港澳地區業務期間，使用了一幅未包含台灣、藏南（印度阿魯納恰爾邦，北京聲稱擁有主權）、阿克賽欽地區和南海諸島的地圖。有關照片當晚在大陸汽車業界流傳，並引起網民大為不滿，認為有宣揚分裂中國之嫌，紛紛要求湧入奧迪中國的官方微博，要求對方致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1710000/1711773/0317002_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1710000%2F1711773%2F0317002_1024.jpg&h=e9c32970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奧迪記者會日前使用的「中國地圖」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1710000/1711773/0317006_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1710000%2F1711773%2F0317006_1024.jpg&h=297a43e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與人民日報使用的中國地圖（右），奧迪所展示的地圖（左）缺少台灣、藏南等地區。<br />\n<br />\n回應網民：我們有中國心<br />\n<br />\n奧迪中國昨日在官方微博網發表聲明，稱奧迪年度全球記者會「展示了一張錯誤的地圖，此舉傷害了中國人民的感情，這是一個嚴重的錯誤。奧迪對此深表歉意，這更是個深刻的教訓，奧迪將引以為戒」。不過，有網民質疑道歉誠意不夠，要求奧迪全球總部給出解釋。奧迪中國回隨即回覆稱「自己也有一顆同樣的中國心」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞報道指出，有業內人士表示，類似「錯誤地圖」也曾於奧迪2015年全球年會上，當時有人提醒奧迪，但並未引起重視。但有分析人士稱，奧迪向來是將大陸和港澳地區銷量合併，而將台灣地區另算。<br />\n<br />\n去年底開始銷量下滑<br />\n<br />\n據該篇已被移除的文章稱，奧迪中國於2009年成立，是奧迪股份公司的全資子公司，主要負責協調奧迪股份公司、一汽集團和一汽&middot;大眾合資公司之間的業務合作事宜場等。資料顯示，去年奧迪在中國大陸銷量超過59萬輛，中國大陸已成為奧迪品牌全球市場份額佔比最大的市場，但近來銷量顯著下滑。自去年11月，奧迪突然宣布將在中國成立新的合資公司「上汽奧迪」開始，引發一汽大眾-奧迪經銷商抱團反對。今年起，奧迪在華銷量已連續兩個月落後平治與寶馬品牌。<br />\n<br />\n另據中國經濟網報道，奧迪董事會成員馮德睿前日在記者會上示，奧迪在華近月銷量「臨時性下降」是因為經銷商感到不安所致。下降趨勢尚不清楚是否會影響今年全年發展。"},{"pid":"b579f5b74b25466e73178dfc6146d5b3cd3a35b1","tid":160326,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d2050a72cbeae609f96fa600571c9b7aa00088","tid":160326,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"Audi 冇撚用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8505c8821080f0db7deed834547aeb376b7e5f2","tid":160326,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b934b0afb9eecb00273f33e19e748194cf1413ac","tid":160326,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fff6e9357f95fb0bd7145fa3128dd4227a04a7","tid":160326,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bf311b5e2e8bae80c66784fe311e3a5d9776d2","tid":160326,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:18:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4b25c164209fff87932c0dec5c6cce1a24e6c15","tid":160326,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:42:28.000Z","msg":"支那AV 精神勝利法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cdf423b9a1364806fbc91177210ae09b84a1f15","tid":160326,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫人改咁多次都係唔會令台灣係中共名下㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594d43554ff4501bae0a2825568e449f0aeda899","tid":160326,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://clipartbarn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/World-map-america-map-solid-clipart-kid.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fclipartbarn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FWorld-map-america-map-solid-clipart-kid.gif&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=3e0cdef7\" target=\"_blank\">http://clipartbarn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/World-map-america-map-solid-clipart-kid.gif</a><br />\n<br />\n中國，一點也不能少！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45165710b1c07e58e025e863a78712043c167fc","tid":160326,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:58:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://clipartbarn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/World-map-america-map-solid-clipart-kid.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fclipartbarn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FWorld-map-america-map-solid-clipart-kid.gif&h=f0db4d15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國，一點也不能少！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0ff92f4c1674bf589be6837c04ff9014f293b5b4","tid":160326,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T18:00:28.000Z","msg":"又傷害感情<img sr